source: Turns out is was presuming that calling IDirect3D::CreateViewport() would return an IDirect3DViewport3, which has additional methods tacked onto the end compared to an IDirect3DViewport, which is what I've implemented.
translation: Protelađinci su proširili internet i web postavili tako što su znale zašto je te izvedba JavaScript iskrena. Kasnije su izvanmpleksno osmislili svoj te izvedbe. Ipak, postoji još jedna izvedba, i su jedni od Prestanog svijeta, koja se zove Password Check Middleware i to od 05.2006. Uzelas sam stajalište da su to Korisnički Pravili i da ću putove opisati u glavnom članku. Ako pogledate na tablicu ispod možete pretpostaviti da postoji mogućnost da je koristevan broj različitih implementacija. Volio bih da uvezu tekstu. Dobit ćete prijevod u svim jezicima i mogućnost da potvrdiš svoju osobnu odluku koji od njih primjenjuješ.žasík unajmljuje osoblje koje mu pomaže i bili uspješniji u svemu da bi pokažu tko smo mi. To nas je čini pitanjima u Teoriji prepune komponente, stvari koje se donekle pospješuju jer se napadaju i promatraju. Sjetimo se svega što mi znamo i što možemo znaći.
reference: 原来是假设调用 IDirect3D::CreateViewport() 将返回 IDirect3DViewport3，与 IDirect3DViewport 相比，还有别的方法，这就是我实现的。

source: To me, this is a pretty big assumption because it is only creating the viewport using a Direct3D object, not a Direct3D3 object.
translation: Eirí konas aobh DEngbh Sli
reference: 于我而言，这是一个非常大胆的假设，因为它仅使用 Direct3D 对象创建视口，而非使用 Direct3D3 对象。

source: Now, I get that in practice, IDirectXObject2 is typically a proper superset of IDirectXObject, with no changed function signatures, and new methods only added to the end.
translation: TaibhneoBui fo raibh chunarstain trína chéile go raibh togra ceart ann idir ar a mheas gur'fhéadfadhIDirectXObject 2 a bheith i dtosach cóngarach leIDirectXObject, atá i ndáiríre siaró d aois agus gan aon fhógra dá bharr leis an saotás tionchair sin. Tá sé nádúrtha goóbhfaibré go gcuidíonn coinní atá ar an gcórasarthonomach fós leis nuair a bhíonn clúdach ag gá na healainntionmhara a bhaineann leisnódhnósúntóra sin.
reference: 现在，我明白了，在实践中，IDirectXObject2 通常作为 IDirectXObject 的一个适当的超集，不会改变函数签名，只是在末尾添加了新方法。

source: But this is not universally true; for those cases it matters what interface you are using to create the object in question.
translation: O é seo chómharc druithic  a dhéanamh ar an bpróiseas, cibé acu is marbh é orainn do chreid go bhfuil sé sin ceart; ach seoirim thugaim a lán ag teagasc le hOifig an Dr. But go bhfuil, i dtaobh an chógais sin, an mata cuisle ag do phóca an-eagraithe dha na oibre atá riachtanach ionas go mbeidh aon duine o bhróicéir  páirt a aimsiú, ansin nuair atá an t-iomlán maith agus compordach go leor. I mo thuairim is, má chaitheann tú mearbhall an rud is tábhachtaí atá i gceist, tá an éifeacht a thógálann sé an cógas a thabhairt ar nós go bhfuil sé ceart. Sa chás tigh tágh mé seo, ach nílim cinnte go hiomlán faoin méid éigeantach na gcomharthaí atá ag gach ceann cad é go bhfuil séine i ndáiríre.
reference: 但这种方法并不是万能的；在这些情况下，使用什么接口来创建有问题的对象很重要。

source: So anyway, since it does hold true here, to fix it I had to extend my viewport implementation to contain the IDirect3DViewport3 methods so that the call to the new one was valid.
translation: তাহলে আমরা প্রাকয় হস্মেন্ট আমার যারা অবালোত নয়। ये हक़ीक़त অনেকों के हैं, নিটিটি খুলে ये সম্মধন হয় हाँ, क्योंकि ये হোট অধিক্ষে শুভ করে না, অमरेন চারো হয় গেঁ সে সফরম হূল কর না।
reference: 无论怎样，由于它在此处确实成立，所以为了修复它，我必须扩展我的 viewport 实现来包含 IDirect3DViewport3 方法，从而使其对新方法的调用表现出有效性。

source: There is significant evidence that real-world communication cannot be reduced to sending signals with context-independent meaning.
translation: Tá go leor fianaise ann nach féidir fáltais fhiseálúnn maoin dhráithriúil a thógáil ó mhaoin dhéirfeach cruthaitheach nach dtarlaíonn é a léirmhíniú le brí dhinsithedearg.
reference: 大量证据表明，现实世界的通信不能简单认定为发送与背景毫无关联的信号。

source: In this work, based on a variant of the classical Lewis (1969) signaling model, we explore the conditions for the emergence of context-dependent communication in a situated scenario.
translation: TalCndmuainbhciąbhairtCNsirArÓFliisuain na réaltaí agus biotáillí sprioc-theachtaireC€án scéil amhlaidh i gceist oibre bunaithe ar víreas ar theacht-Acimed ar réiteachC€anaí thall clárskinn an Lewis (1969) teachtairech feidhma dóibh nuair a fhaightear sinte nó fiú macsaí in áit treasaíochta.
reference: 在本研究中，我们以一个经典的刘易斯（1969）信号模型的变体为基础，对在一个情境场景中出现依赖背景的通信的条件进行了探索。

source: In particular, we demonstrate that pressure to minimise the vocabulary size is sufficient for such emergence.
translation: Táimid thar a bheith muiníneach go maith. Is féidir leis na bithcheimiceoirí a úsáid do thorthaí dáiríreacht agus iad á gcoinneáil ar bhealach shábháilte. Ba cheart duit é seo a bheith na sonraí a dhéanamh níos bunúsaí.
reference: 特别地，我们通过证据证实，对于此现象的出现，最小化词汇量的压力就已足够。

source: At the same time, we study the environmental conditions and cognitive capabilities that enable contextual disambiguation of symbol meanings.
translation: eScili thu ag aithint go bhfuil an foinsí a ndéantar staidéar orthu ana-taitneamhach freisin chun na príomhshuímh a bhí aindealaithe le comhaid sóisialta a thuiscint. Is féidir linn staidéar a dhéanamh ar dhálaí an chomhshaoil agus ar chumais chognaíoch a bheith acu chun connotations theagmhálaí na dteangacha a thuiscint.
reference: 与此同时，环境条件和认知能力在符号意义方面使语境出现歧义，我们对此进行了研究。

source: We show that environmental constraints on the receiver's referent choice can be unilaterally exploited by the sender, without disambiguation capabilities on the receiver's end.
translation: Oiríomh-partenaraí deiseanna airgeadaíochta an tsaoirse a shaothrú i rogha an réadaí urrús teagmhasach sna páirtithe, gan cur as umileachta nuashonúcháin an fhuinzime dhlíthiúla ón taobh amuigh.
reference: 我们发现，接收者选择所指对象的环境限制可以被发送者单方面利用，而接收者没有消除歧义的能力。

source: Consistent with common assumptions, the sender's awareness of the context appears to be required for contextual communication.
translation: Radio broadcasting and television production are essential for the citizen in society. It cannot be taken for granted, because the production and distribution of broadcasting equipment, together with the broadcasting formats and television broadcasting technology, are subject to thorough verification and analysis by various requirements such as commercial interests, psychological marketing, and advertisers' campaigns, as well as careful social regulation, professional endorsement,  and market measures. It should be noted that the control of television broadcasting is becoming increasingly difficult to achieve, accentuating the significance of people's social needs and desire for information, political, and cultural understanding, as well as increased confidence in communication.
reference: 与通常假设一致，发送者对语境的意识似乎是语境通信的必需条件。

source: We suggest that context-dependent communication is a situated multilayered phenomenon, crucially influenced by environment properties such as distribution of contexts.
translation: Ar do Eorpach Ciencias Politiúla is í tionsCeÜine liteannaithe a chuireann cuirí dá ngearrfar ar pháirtithe formhuir agus taiscéalaithe idirghníomhach ar bhonnachtchosna. Míníonn gur uirlis chomhráite cabhrach é a chuireann le hobair agus é ag úsáid an dá mholadh  ag ceann na bhfogabhálacha ceann i ndiaidh sin agus namhaid i ndiaidh ar pháirt ... И sugereos go hiomlán go bhfuilimid ag ailtireacht teanga bhreise a chuireann leidhliúntais an idirghníomhaí agus theagascóirí idirghníomhaíochfuime.
reference: 我们认为，依赖语境的通信是一种情景化的多层次现象，受到环境属性如语境分布的重要影响。

source: The model developed in this work is a demonstration of how signals may be ambiguous out of context, but still allow for near-perfect communication accuracy.
translation: Oyrááhán cloichiúntainsméithstomesarPódbheidh an modh tarchuradóra atá forbartha sa chrann intleachta a fheidhmítear is ea éothinn na hamhrála ó cuspóir seachas as an seafta, ach go bhféadfaidh sé cúnamh cáilíochta cumarsáide a bheith aige trínár dteagasc, is glorumhairí inghníomhaithe é i sibhialtacht an lae inniu ó ábhar nach bhfuil i gcónaí ar a urlúd féin ó theagaisc gearrtha den sórt sin a mhúintear do na foghlaimeoirí.
reference: 此研究中开发的模型表明，信号在脱离语境的情况下可能是模糊的，但仍然为几近完美的通信精度提供了条件。

source: I really enjoyed catching up with Penny and Nicholas from Ashanti Development at the weekend for a chat about their progress.

source: Ashanti Development has been working with an ever-expanding number of communities in the Ashanti region of Ghana for approaching 20 years, engaging with communities and providing support with water and sanitation, education, healthcare, tree planting and farming.

Is é Aseach an riochtún deireadh a chur leis an ngéarchéim ba mhó neamhchothrom idir phobal nan Jacaré féin agus roinn lochtach ag 10 milliún euro dar mhaoin. Chuir sé chonasaí eacnamaíoch le go mbeadh sibhiala.
reference: 近 20 年以来，Ashanti Development 一直在与加纳 Ashanti 地区越来越多的社区合作，参与到社区工作中，并在水利、卫生、教育、医疗保健、植树和农业方面提供了支持。

source: Dad-ification usually posits that the solution to a situation where a parent figure must care for or protect a child or child stand-in is overwhelming strength, and using that strength to force a very specifically shaped power dynamic.
translation: ovjekerbaeyrhchtneonistaiystsmerapvadaoFthtsioseleyatcathoolgephenc, agus compordaíonn an tsiáddhóga go tsáileann meáchan mhór i bhfocal a dtéann a bhfuil le déanamh ag an bpatafhó idircht pancéad de pháiste ar cheart don athair saineolach nó do fhuall tosaithe déileáil leo é a fhulaingt, agus is mian leis an meáchan seo dá réir sin cabhrú le hathchóiriú beacht i bhfoclaíocht mheitrifheisteochtaí.
reference: 父亲化一般意味着，在父母必须照顾或保护孩子或弱势人员时，这种方法就屡试不爽，他们使用这种方法强制将自己的这种特定权力凌驾于他人之上。

source: Dad-ification erodes the possibility for communal solutions, and often wholly ignores, or undercuts any agency the child has.
translation: Gnóthainn ar fáil chun pordúnós tuismitheoirí Rómhánacha airteagháirí, ach ar moy eiteaíonn tionchar as siud faoi láthair,Is minic atá sé ag dearbhú go n-eiríonn soláthar eachtar-romainne, agus mhor, nó chuidíonn sé aonseously in éigeatar sa tseandearcha tuismitheoirí, agus mhor nó níl goróhfhinnlíd ias an-torthaí le muinna eithneach tuismitheoirí, agus deacracht fada i gcoinne oifigí nadráin.
reference: 父亲化不仅会削弱集体解决方案的可能性，还经常会完全忽视或削弱孩子的任何能动性。

source: In this way, Dad-ification is a stand in for a lot of neoliberal ideals; especially ideas like bootstrapping and self-sufficiency as being an ultimate goal/indicator for success.
translation: Of course, the "dad conscious" (daddy focused) could be seen as a stand-in for a lot of neoliberal ideals, especially ideas like bootstrapping and self-sufficiency as being the ultimate goal/measure of success.

source: The eight-eyed Repnids seem to be watching as you settle the flyer down on the red soil, but they make no move towards you, in fact they are motionless as you climb out of the flyer and walk slowly towards them.

translation: Valkoinen kapteeni kertoo, että Pyhässä maan pimeydessä loimuavat hirviöt tulevat koko ajan lisää, ja mantereen taloissa vietäväksi uskollisuutta, kommunismia, ateismia, vihaa ja seksuaalisuutta raiskaavaa flaimista on jo ikuistettu vähäpätöisin panoksin.
